uveaux cas confirm\u00e9s \u00e0 Oued Souf - Alg\u00e9rie360.com|date=2020-03-18|website=www.algerie360.com|language=fr|access-date=2020-03-21}}</ref>\n\nOn 19 March, ten new confirmed cases of the COVID-19, including two new deaths, to reach a total of 82 confirmed cases including eight deaths.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://covid19.sante.gov.dz/fr/2020/03/19/suivi-quotidien-du-coronavirus-covid-19-jeudi-19-mars-2020/|title=Suivi quotidien du Coronavirus COVID-19 Jeudi 19 mars 2020 \u2013 Minist\u00e8re de la Sant\u00e9 de la Population et de la R\u00e9forme Hospitali\u00e8re avec la contribution du Minist\u00e8re de la Poste et des T\u00e9l\u00e9communications|language=fr-FR|access-date=2020-03-19}}</ref> The same day, a ninth death is recorded in the [[M\u00e9d\u00e9a Province]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.observalgerie.com/coronavirus-lalgerie-enregistre-un-neuvieme-deces/2020/|title=Coronavirus : L'Alg\u00e9rie enregistre un neuvi\u00e8me d\u00e9c\u00e8s|date=2020-03-19|website=Observ'Alg\u00e9rie|language=fr-FR|access-date=2020-03-20}}</ref> a 47-year-old man (Former Algerian judo player Othman Tijani)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.beurfm.net/news/coronavirus-deces-du-judoka-algerien-othman-tijani-21135|title=Coronavirus : d\u00e9c\u00e8s du judoka alg\u00e9rien Othman Tijani - Beur FM|website=www.beurfm.net|access-date=2020-03-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.saudi24.news/2020/03/the-death-of-an-algerian-athlete-with-corona-virus-sport-arab-and-international.html|title=The death of an Algerian athlete with Corona virus \u2013 sport \u2013 Arab and international|last=admin|date=2020-03-20|website=Saudi 24 News|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tellerreport.com/sports/2020-03-19---the-first-athlete-in-algeria-died-of-the-corona-virus-.Sylob7B-UI.html|title=The first athlete in Algeria died of the Corona virus {{!}} tellerreport.com|last=Anonym|website=www.tellerreport.com|language=en|access-date=2020-03-20}}</ref>\n\nOn 20 March, a tenth death was recorded in Algeria in [[El Oued Province]], it is the sister of the first case of Province.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ennaharonline.com/%d8%aa%d8%b3%d8%ac%d9%8a%d9%84-%d8%ad%d8%a7%d9%84%d8%a9-%d9%88%d9%81%d8%a7%d8%a9-%d8%ac%d8%af%d9%8a%d8%af%d8%a9-%d8%a8%d9%81%d9%8a%d8%b1%d9%88%d8%b3-%d9%83%d9%88%d8%b1%d9%88%d9%86%d8%a7-%d9%81%d9%8a-2/|title=\u062a\u0633\u062c\u064a\u0644 \u062d\u0627\u0644\u0629 \u0648\u0641\u0627\u0629 \u062c\u062f\u064a\u062f\u0629 \u0628\u0641\u064a\u0631\u0648\u0633 \u0643\u0648\u0631\u0648\u0646\u0627 \u0641\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0648\u0627\u062f\u064a \u0648\u0627\u0644\u062d\u0635\u064a\u0644\u0629 \u062a\u0631\u062a\u0641\u0639 \u0625\u0644\u0649 10|date=2020-03-20|website=\u0627\u0644\u0646\u0647\u0627\u0631 \u0623\u0648\u0646\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0646|language=ar|access-date=2020-03-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.algerie360.com/coronavirus-en-algerie-un-deuxieme-deces-a-el-oued/|title=Coronavirus en Alg\u00e9rie : Un deuxi\u00e8me d\u00e9c\u00e8s \u00e0 El Oued - Alg\u00e9rie360.com|date=2020-03-20|website=www.algerie360.com|language=fr|access-date=2020-03-20}}</ref> The death (11th) of a 77-year-old woman  has been announced in [[Azeffoun]], [[Tizi Ouzou Province|Tizi-Ouzou Province]], bringing the death toll from the virus to 11 in Algeria.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.echoroukonline.com/%d9%81%d9%8a%d8%b1%d9%88%d8%b3-%d9%83%d9%88%d8%b1%d9%88%d9%86%d8%a7-%d8%a7%d8%b1%d8%aa%d9%81%d8%a7%d8%b9-%d8%b9%d8%af%d8%af-%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%88%d9%81%d9%8a%d8%a7%d8%aa-%d9%81%d9%8a-%d8%a7%d9%84%d8%ac/|title=\u0641\u064a\u0631\u0648\u0633 \u0643\u0648\u0631\u0648\u0646\u0627: \u0627\u0631\u062a\u0641\u0627\u0639 \u0639\u062f\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0648\u0641\u064a\u0627\u062a \u0641\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0632\u0627\u0626\u0631 \u0625\u0644\u0649 11 \u062d\u0627\u0644\u0627\u062a|date=2020-03-20|website=\u0627\u0644\u0634\u0631\u0648\u0642 \u0623\u0648\u0646\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0646|language=ar|access-da